The paper discusses the development of a question-answering system using natural language understanding and intent classification. This falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of machine learning and deep learning methods for intent classification also falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of text vector representations, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
